name: I'm A-MAZE-ING
description: In my younger days, I tend to force my self to be more approachable, so that I can have more friends. It was until I realized that can be so exhausting. Turns out I was more of a reserved person who enjoys lots of alone time. So, now, I am not letting anybody get in to my head (or life) easily. I like my circle small, I guess. And that's OK! :)
